OUR PRODUCT

Delivering Conviction in Great Outcomes

We’re passionate about building companies the right way as opposed to rolling the dice or shooting for the moon. As a result, we view our portfolio partnerships as owner-operators, not as portfolio managers. We’re committed to driving the BEST risk-adjusted outcomes and preservation of optionality at every node in the company development journey enabled by an iterative approach to growth.

Delivering Tangible Impact

Impact extending multiple layers and “product” capabilities. The investment team brings hyper-specialization as a strategic consigliere and deep consultative bench given all of the experience is concentrated in the emerging growth stage and in the vertical markets we cover. Supported by a best-in-class proprietary technology stack and deep advisory and expert community.
